    content:
      "\u003cp\u003eThe Aeronaut 8000 Combat badminton racket features a medium flex shaft combined with an aerodynamic frame for rear court power, speed and accuracy\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eAeronaut racket technology is geared towards ultimate precision and control. A unique air-stream channel integrated into the racket head reduces air resistance which helps to generate faster shuttlecock speeds. It’s suitable for players looking for the best control with little to no sacrifice in power.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFEATURES\u003c/strong\u003e:\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWing Stabiliser\u003c/strong\u003e - Aviation technology that stabilises frame vibration to improve comfort, control and racket recovery.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTB-Nano\u003c/strong\u003e - Designed for improved power transfer, nanometer technology binds carbon-fiber and resin more tightly, allowing grater stability, elasticity and durability.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDynamic-Optimum Frame\u003c/strong\u003e - This unique head-design, enlarges the sweet-spot of the racket. It allows for more consistent and higher hitting velocity, without sacrificing durability.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHot Melt\u003c/strong\u003e - The resin distributed more uniformly and closely combined with the carbon fibre by using the Hot Melt. It improves the strength and provides the same excellent using experience.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCubic Locking\u003c/strong\u003e - Cubic grommet locked within the slim groove is more stable and could provide extra protection for string, effectively absorb shock to get an accurate placement, improve controlling performance.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMPCF Reinforcing Tech\u003c/strong\u003e - Multi-layer carbon fibres combine with exquisite handicraft to strengthen the racket whilst ensuring there are no wrinkles in the material during machine processing. This improves racket perfromance and durability\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAero Tec-Beam System\u003c/strong\u003e - Based on aerodynamics, support of advanced calculation and gathering practising data, the racket frame has an extremely low drag coefficient and high intensity to provide maximum speed and improve players' performance in various shots.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFATP Tech\u003c/strong\u003e - By changing the shaft flex point, quickening rebound speed, rackets featuring FATP return to position quickly and ready for the continuous attack\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStabilised Elastic Shaft\u003c/strong\u003e - Aramid fibre is a high modulus, high strength material with good elasticity and toughness. It's the main material in helmets and body armour. The slim shaft, filled with aramid fibre helps to reduce vibrations that could cause sports injuries.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUHB Shaft\u003c/strong\u003e - Combining cutting-edge scientific and technological achievements with the measured data of players, the ergonomic principle is used to continuously adjust the performance of the shaft to improve its bending point and smash performance.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e *Please note that all Li-Ning rackets require a custom restring as they are not strung by the manufacturer. \u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBadmintonHQ is an authorised Li-Ning stockist and all Li-Ning products sold by us are 100% genuine\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e",
