    content:
      "\u003cp\u003eThe\u003cstrong\u003e Li-Ning BladeX 900 Moon Max Badminton Racket \u003c/strong\u003eis a professional racket, designed for serious players. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSporting a stunning blue and black design, and coming with premium packaging, the BladeX 900 makes an impact before it's even reached the court. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAn even-balance racket, the BladeX is incredibly responsive, allowing you to react quickly to any shot you receive, and the swing weight technology will transfer the weight of the racket into your returns, making them more offensive and lethal for your opponent to deal with. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWith a stiff shaft flex and the potential to be strung at up to 31 lbs of tension, this racket can be insanely precise, giving advanced players ultimate control over their shots. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFeatures:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHDF Shock Absorbing System - \u003c/strong\u003eHigh-tech, shock-absorbing materials used to reduce vibrations and impact, reducing injuries on powerful shots and transferring power more smoothly. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUltra Carbon - \u003c/strong\u003eUltra strong material, giving the racket a premium quality feel with higher strength, rigidity and durability. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAccele Tech - \u003c/strong\u003eEnhances rebound performance, making shots easier to pull off with power, without sacrificing control. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDynamic-Optimum Frame - \u003c/strong\u003eProduces a larger sweet spot, increasing velocity and power, making shots easier to hit. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWing Stabiliser - \u003c/strong\u003eAviation technology to reduce vibration and improve precision. \u003c/p\u003e",
